{
  "stem": "26728.7",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know how the British talk about the bloody this, the bloody that and their slang.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had the bloody [INAUDIBLE] or whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's dragging a-- a prisoner by the foot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A dead-- a dead-- a dead whatever they called them, a corpse, by the foot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, I yelled at him to pick him up and he didn't pay-- and he was in civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said he had a hat on, like a-- like a dress hat, and a-- and a black suit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I yelled at him, he said, and he ignored me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He just kept walking on with his-- dragging this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, I got so mad, I went over there and hit him with my rifle butt and brained him on the spot.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, you brained him?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, brains all over the place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was just happy as hell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, well who was he?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some people took him away in a cart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was going to throw him in the hole, he says, but some people, probably his family, took him out of the camp in a cart and probably buried him.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he said, the guy was like-- you know, I'm standing there aghast.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And hitting a man with a rifle butt is-- is you can easily brain him if you know how to do it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh, and that was-- that-- Bergen-Belsen, from the standpoint of-- of total blowing you away, of seeing this is-- this is where what you see is unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To see bulldozers pushing thousands of corpses into deep holes, pouring lime on top of them-- on them-- layers and layers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean these are not just one layer.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
